{"word":"G1977 - ἐπιῤῥίπτω - epirrhíptō - ep-ir-hrip'-to - Cast upon","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπιῤῥίπτω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">epirrhíptō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ep-ir-hrip'-to</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Cast upon</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - போடு, வைத்துவிடு"},{"paragraph":"to throw upon, place upon"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1909 - ἐπί - epí - ep-ee'/1909\">G1909</a> and <a href=\"#/G4496 - ῥίπτω - rhíptō - hrip'-to/4496\">G4496</a>; to <i>throw upon</i> (literally or figuratively): - cast upon.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1977/1977\">G1977</a>, <a href=\"#/G4495/4495\">G4495</a>, <a href=\"#/G4496/4496\">G4496</a>, <a href=\"#/G641/641\">G641</a>"}]}